            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報21150點，跌79點，較上日現貨收市價21056點高水93點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報4820點，跌34點，高水24點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報7818點，跌15點，高水39點。</p>\n</div>",
