        {
            "title": "卓悅折讓25.93%進行1供3籌最多1.07億元 大股東以股東貸款抵銷 公司淨集資約5200萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">卓悅控股(00653)公布，擬1供3集資最多1.07億元，供股價0.08元，較該股昨天收市價0.108元折讓25.93%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：卓悅控股官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230828_FI_source-web_00653.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：卓悅控股官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230828_FI_source-web_00653.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：卓悅控股官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價0.111元計，供股價較之折讓27.93%。以該股去年底時未經審核綜合資產淨值1約0.332元計，供股價較之折讓達75.91%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">雖然供股集資額達1.07億元，但由於大股東陳健文將以卓悅所欠的股東貸款下尚未償還本金及應計利息約5639萬元，抵銷認購供股所需的5402萬元，故卓悅從供股實際集資淨額僅5200萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">卓悅擬將集資淨額5200萬元當中約2500萬元，用於升級現有跨境電商平台香港貓；約1500萬元用於提升批發產品業務模式的投資；約1200萬元撥作一般營運資金。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14860832-%e5%8d%93%e6%82%85%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%9325-93%e9%80%b2%e8%a1%8c1%e4%be%9b3%e7%b1%8c%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%9a1-07%e5%84%84%e5%85%83-%e5%a4%a7%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e4%bb%a5%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e8%b2%b8%e6%ac%be",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source-web_00653-2024-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 08:45:42",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期守於21000點之上輕微低水 重磅港股ADR互有升跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時12分升85點或0.41%，報21053點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報21035點，較香港上日現貨收市低21點或0.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣448.6元，較上日香港收市高0.64元或0.14%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣103.6元，較上日香港收市低1.83元或1.73%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣135元，較上日香港收市高0.08元或0.06%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣137.1元，較上日香港收市低1.28元或0.93%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣41.1元，較上日香港收市低0.13元或0.31%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣80.7元，較上日香港收市高1.14元或1.44%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣52.8元，較上日香港收市高0.07元或0.13%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣328.6元，較上日香港收市高0.96元或0.29%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣43.3元，較上日香港收市高0.01元或0.03%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣6.5元，較上日香港收市低0.01元或0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報21008點，跌221點，較上日恒指收市21056點，低水49點。科指期貨夜市收報4762點，較上日科指收市低水34點；國指期貨夜市收報7752點，較上日國指收市低水27點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14860824-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%ae%88%e6%96%bc21000%e9%bb%9e%e4%b9%8b%e4%b8%8a%e8%bc%95%e5%be%ae%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e4%ba%92%e6%9c%89%e5%8d%87%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 08:20:43",
